Key Match Events: In a notable 118-115 victory against the Minnesota Timberwolves, Boston was led by Jayson Tatum's 33 points and Derrick White's 26 points.
Jayson Tatum contributed significantly with nine assists and eight rebounds, showcasing his all-around game.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Celtics' victory against the Timberwolves marked the beginning of a four-game road trip, providing a much-needed boost after struggling with an 8-6 record in December.
